{"tid":1630924,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家唔好見係老account就咁老定","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:03:37.000Z","uid":4281,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"b2dfee89094a0cf4e9807184d1548e06a59d9799","tid":1630924,"uid":4281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:08:32.000Z","msg":"個人意見<br />\n就算唔係P牌<br />\n但宜家好多義士畀狗捉左<br />\n手機開左鎖既話,狗就可以唔洗登入就可以喺連登出post<br />\n大家一定要自己有理性分析<br />\n我都見好多巴絲都好醒同鎮定咁回應<br />\n所以淨係善用起底之外,仲要醒目咁留意另類五毛 !<br />\n<br />\n好似呢個user<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1630093/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1630093/page/1</a><br />\n對上一個post係一年前出<br />\n跟手今日就連續出3個post,仲建議裝修一d無共識、過火位既鋪<br />\n好有機會係狗背後想影響個運動不利於我地<br />\n大家要小心<br />\n要同政府潛藏o既心理學家、團隊、狗捏過 !"},{"pid":"29b2c3b4c75c90e25aa6479eb7222c06ab4b2920","tid":1630924,"uid":4281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e53ed79d43757de393d3956f8edf72350806998","tid":1630924,"uid":4281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34af36710e70ac80b6a8d913e53c2fedea8a29f6","tid":1630924,"uid":4281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9d6976fbe5f135ca54d1a4b395730aff8ddb061","tid":1630924,"uid":258696,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:11:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"886ed0c2fb106a55df99afdc1fe0230261c1727f","tid":1630924,"uid":4281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:11:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"068ada955026fe1c46ecf12f3233a34619807e15","tid":1630924,"uid":4281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:12:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d44291638e0d1ce1b0f3a83e66855ce880dffa09","tid":1630924,"uid":4281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c589784a009df46cfb2effe342f3de048215ab66","tid":1630924,"uid":73945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n呢幾日鬼account 超多"},{"pid":"f8a5ef65574cf51a2ecec7430a526b9171176ae6","tid":1630924,"uid":4281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3471de73ecf4bcc8dbcd7623153166e7901cd32","tid":1630924,"uid":69294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:14:47.000Z","msg":"＿巴打,呢樣野我都懷疑左一段時間<br />\n比人沒收電話既手足,請立即將所有密碼改晒佢<br />\n連登改PW會登出晒所有login既device<br />\n＿同埋我懷疑有一班臥底潛伏左好耐扮手足,必要時就幫手帶方向<br />\n＿人地空姐都識扮黃,去25D 真黃同事.所以請大家要有批判性思考"},{"pid":"4f015f873ee960950d92cc75df61d018fff5fc3